quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,135,"Baranavuze bati “Nimube Abayahudi (Abayahudi babwira abakurikiye Intumwa Muhamadi)! Cyangwa Abanaswara<sup>1</sup> (Abanaswara babwira abakurikiye Intumwa Muhamadi) ni bwo muzayoboka!” Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ahubwo (ukuyoboka nyako ni ugukurikira) idini ritunganye rya Aburahamu (Ibrahim) (ritabangikanya Imana), kandi ntiyari mu babangikanyamana.","[1] Reba uko twasobanuye iyi nyito mu murongo wa 62 muri Surat ul Baqarat"
  2,136,"(Yemwe Bayisilamu) muvuge muti “Twemeye Allah n’ibyo twahishuriwe, n’ibyahishuriwe Aburahamu (Ibrahimu), Ishimayeli (Ismail), Isaka (Is’haq), Yakobo (Yaqub) n’urubyaro rwe, ibyahishuriwe Musa, ibyahishuriwe Yesu (Issa) ndetse n’ibyahishuriwe abahanuzi biturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo. Nta n’umwe tuvangura muri bo kandi ni We twicishaho bugufi.”",""
  2,137,"Bityo nibemera nk’ibyo mwemeye bazaba bayobotse, ariko nibabitera umugongo, bazaba bari mu macakubiri. Allah azabagutsindira kandi ni na We Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje.",""
  2,138,"(Dukurikira) kamere ndemano (idini) ya Allah. Ni iyihe kamere ndemano yaruta iya Allah (yaremanye abantu)? Ni na we twe tugaragira.",""
  2,139,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese muratugisha impaka kuri Allah kandi ari we Nyagasani wacu akaba na Nyagasani wanyu? Kandi dufite ibikorwa byacu namwe mukagira ibyanyu, ndetse ni na We twiyegurira.",""
  2,140,"Cyangwa muvuga ko mu by’ukuri, Ibrahim, Ismail, Is’haq, Yaqub n’urubyaro rwe bari Abayahudi cyangwa Abanaswara?<sup>1</sup> Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese ni mwe mubizi cyane cyangwa ni Allah (ubizi kubarusha)?” Ni nde muhemu kurusha uhisha ubuhamya afite (buri mu gitabo cye) buturuka kwa Allah? Kandi Allah ntabwo ayobewe ibyo mukora.","[1] Reba uko twasobanuye iyi nyito mu murongo wa 62 muri Surat ul Baqarat."
  2,141,"Uwo ni umuryango (Umat) wahise; ufite ibyo wakoze namwe mufite ibyo mwakoze (buri wese azahemberwa ibyo yakoze). Kandi ntimuzabazwa ibyo bakoraga.",""
